    {
      "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s41598-026-42859-4-pdf",
      "@type": [
        "ArtigoCientifico",
        "schema:ScholarlyArticle"
      ],
      "arquivo": "s41598-026-42859-4.pdf",
      "titulo": "QRGEC: quantum reinforcement",
      "temObjetivo": [
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s41598-026-42859-4-pdf/objetivo/1",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "objetivo",
          "ordem": 1,
          "texto": "To address these challenges, this research proposes QRGEC: Quantum Reinforcement Learning with Golden Jackal Optimization for Resilient Edge Cloud Coordination in Internet Computing."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s41598-026-42859-4-pdf/objetivo/2",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "objetivo",
          "ordem": 2,
          "texto": "The proposed hybrid framework integrates quantum focused policy exploration with adaptive metaheuristic tuning to enhance distributed Internet computing optimization."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s41598-026-42859-4-pdf/objetivo/3",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "objetivo",
          "ordem": 3,
          "texto": "Developing methods such as quantum reinforcement learning provides promising opportunities to mitigate these challenges."
        }
      ],
      "temProblema": [
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s41598-026-42859-4-pdf/problema/1",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "problema",
          "ordem": 1,
          "texto": "However, to the best of our knowledge, no existing work has combined QRL with GJO for enhancing the resilience and coordination efficiency of edge-cloud systems under fluctuating computational and communication constraints."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s41598-026-42859-4-pdf/problema/2",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "problema",
          "ordem": 2,
          "texto": "However, the dynamic heterogeneity within the Internet-scale systems and the stochastic nature of the resources are a major challenge in the effective coordination of the Edge and the cloud layers1."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s41598-026-42859-4-pdf/problema/3",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "problema",
          "ordem": 3,
          "texto": "However, they struggle in environments with changing network topologies and varying resource requirements, thus hindering scalability and dependability in distributed systems."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s41598-026-42859-4-pdf/problema/4",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "problema",
          "ordem": 4,
          "texto": "Outlined networking challenges in distributed quantum computing, emphasizing synchronization, quantum routing, and entanglement-management issues that hinder scalable quantum Internet development19."
        }
      ],
      "temMetodologia": [
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s41598-026-42859-4-pdf/metodo/1",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "metodo",
          "ordem": 1,
          "texto": "Scope of quantum evaluation The quantum reinforcement learning components in QRGEC are evaluated using state-of-the-art quantum simulation platforms, including Qiskit and Tensor Flow Quantum, integrated with Cloud Sim Plus."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s41598-026-42859-4-pdf/metodo/2",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "metodo",
          "ordem": 2,
          "texto": "Performance of the proposed QRGEC framework was verified based on hybrid edge cloud systems, implemented using Cloud Sim Plus 6.0 combined with Qiskit 1.2 and Tensor Flow Quantum libraries through extensive simulations."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s41598-026-42859-4-pdf/metodo/3",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "metodo",
          "ordem": 3,
          "texto": "The quantum reinforcement learning components in QRGEC are implemented using Qiskit and Tensor Flow Quantum simulators."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s41598-026-42859-4-pdf/metodo/4",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "metodo",
          "ordem": 4,
          "texto": "Training was conducted for E = 200 episodes with (λg,λ q)=(0.3, 0.25) and trust bound δ =0.01."
        }
      ],
