    {
      "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s43926-026-00316-8-pdf",
      "@type": [
        "ArtigoCientifico",
        "schema:ScholarlyArticle"
      ],
      "arquivo": "s43926-026-00316-8.pdf",
      "titulo": "RESEARCH Open Access",
      "temObjetivo": [
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s43926-026-00316-8-pdf/objetivo/1",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "objetivo",
          "ordem": 1,
          "texto": "Discover Internet of Things (2026) 6:53 3 Io T-edge coordination layer The Io T-Edge Coordination Layer plays a pivotal role in and this proves optimal task scheduling and resource management across distributed Io T and edge infrastructures. 3.1 Task scheduling framework The goal is to maximize cumulative reward Rt, which balances Qo S, energy efficiency, and throughput."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s43926-026-00316-8-pdf/objetivo/2",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "objetivo",
          "ordem": 2,
          "texto": "The main objectives of the work involve the fol lowing: (1) To design a unified AI-driven quantum-resilient Cyber-Physical System (AIQRCPS) framework."
        }
      ],
      "temProblema": [
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s43926-026-00316-8-pdf/problema/1",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "problema",
          "ordem": 1,
          "texto": "However, as quantum computing and ultra-dense Io T networks tends to get expanded, traditional encrypting data and optimizing systems are insufficient to secure the data in real time."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s43926-026-00316-8-pdf/problema/2",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "problema",
          "ordem": 2,
          "texto": "However, the modern systems struggle with latency management and high computational complexity that occur after quantum computing."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s43926-026-00316-8-pdf/problema/3",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "problema",
          "ordem": 3,
          "texto": "Artificial Intelligence (AI) with post-quantum cryptography and edge intelligence transforms CPS into self-adaptive ecosystems that is capable of handling threats."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s43926-026-00316-8-pdf/problema/4",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "problema",
          "ordem": 4,
          "texto": "Similarly, Elkhodr et al. [27] present the Combined Adaptive Security Framework for Io T (IASF-Io T), which uses AI, blockchain, quantum-resistant cryptog raphy, and Digital Twins for predictive and proactive threat mitigation."
        }
      ],
      "temMetodologia": [
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s43926-026-00316-8-pdf/metodo/1",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "metodo",
          "ordem": 1,
          "texto": "The simulations are configured with the following parameters to model realistic CPS operation as in Tables 12, 13. 6.4 Performance metrics The performance of the proposed framework is evaluated using the following metrics: Average Latency (ms): It measures the end-to-end delay for task execution across edge-Io T-cloud layers."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s43926-026-00316-8-pdf/metodo/2",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "metodo",
          "ordem": 2,
          "texto": "At 50 nodes, the proposed framework achieves 74.5 tasks/s, outperforming FOA (58.7 tasks/s), QML (61.8 tasks/s), QHCP (64.1 tasks/s), and CH-DDQ + 2-Brain (65.8 tasks/s)."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s43926-026-00316-8-pdf/metodo/3",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "metodo",
          "ordem": 3,
          "texto": "Experimental evaluation shows that the proposed framework achieves an average latency as low as 7.9-10.7 ms, throughput up to 94.5 tasks/s, energy consumption as low as 3.3-4.8 J/task, and task completion rates exceeding 98% across varying edge/Io T node densities and bandwidths."
        },
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s43926-026-00316-8-pdf/metodo/4",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "metodo",
          "ordem": 4,
          "texto": "Hence, this paper research develops an AI-Driven Quantum-Resilient Cyber-Physical System (AI-QRCPS) framework that combines three novel layers and this includes: (i) a Post-Quantum Security Layer employing lattice-based cryptography and quantum key distribution for end-to-end confidentiality, (ii) an Adaptive Intelligence Layer using Reinforcement Learning (RL) and Firefly Optimization for dynamic resource orchestration and anomaly detection, and (iii) an Io T-Edge Coordination Layer for latency-aware task scheduling using double deep Q-learning."
        }
      ],
      "temContribuicao": [
        {
          "@id": "http://example.org/trab2-ia/lucas-matheus/quantum-computing-nlp-analysis/artigo/s43926-026-00316-8-pdf/contribuicao/1",
          "@type": "TrechoExtraido",
          "categoria": "contribuicao",
          "ordem": 1,
          "texto": "The novelty involves a three-layered design, which combines quantum-safe cryptog raphy, adaptive learning-based optimization and Io T-edge coordination for security across heterogeneous CPS environments."
        }
      ],
